text.tspan: Cabbage, about fifty jiki loads(a jiki load
would probably be about two bushels.)
Mrs. F.M. Eversole from Chunju, Korea
At last I am sending you ... a recipe for kimchi, which
some of the housekeepers may like to have. It is one
used by Mr. Eversole last fall in filling his silo.
in Korea. Photo sent by Mrs. F.M.
